ZH: 我们在门上挂了一条门帘。
EN: We hung a door curtain on the door.
ZH: 她用一块布做了一个门帘。
EN: She made a door curtain with a piece of fabric.
ZH: 请把门帘拉上，我想要私人空间。
EN: Could you please pull down the door curtain? I want some privacy.
ZH: 妈妈买了一条漂亮的绣花门帘。
EN: Mom bought a beautiful embroidered door curtain.
ZH: 换上门帘后，整个房间看起来明亮多了。
EN: After changing the door curtain, the whole room looks much brighter.
ZH: 每次夏天我们都会把门帘改成透气的凉帘。
EN: Every summer, we change the door curtain to a breathable cool curtain.
ZH: 这是一个羊毛门帘，可以保持房间温暖。
EN: This is a woolen door curtain that can keep the room warm.
ZH: 门帘的颜色与墙壁相配，增加了整个房间的色调。
EN: The color of the door curtain matches the wall, enhancing the overall tone of the room.
ZH: 她拿起门帘，用力地甩了一下，希望把灰尘甩掉。
EN: She picked up the door curtain and shook it vigorously, hoping to shake off the dust.
ZH: 我们的门上挂着一条有吉祥寓意的红色门帘。
EN: There is a red door curtain with auspicious meaning hanging on our door.
ZH: 同时拉开门帘和窗帘，可以增加屋内的通风效果。
EN: Opening both the door curtain and the window curtain at the same time can improve the ventilation in the room.
ZH: 奶奶一直坐在门口的门帘下，享受着阳光的温暖。
EN: Grandma has been sitting under the door curtain at the door, enjoying the warmth of the sun.
ZH: 我在门帘上缝了一朵花，增加了一些装饰性。
EN: I sewed a flower on the door curtain to add some decoration.
ZH: 请把门帘打开，让新鲜空气进来。
EN: Please open the door curtain and let fresh air in.
ZH: 门帘落下时，隔绝了外界的噪音和视线。
EN: When the door curtain falls, it isolates the noise and sight from outside.
ZH: 门帘上的花纹非常精致，展示了艺术细节。
EN: The pattern on the door curtain is very delicate, showcasing artistic details.
ZH: 我们的门帘是手工制作的，每一个花朵都是用心绣制的。
EN: Our door curtain is handmade, and each flower is embroidered with care.
ZH: 她暂时用门帘遮挡住阳光，让房间保持凉爽。
EN: She temporarily blocked the sunlight with the door curtain to keep the room cool.
ZH: 我的门帘已经用了很多年，该换一条新的了。
EN: My door curtain has been used for many years. It's time to get a new one.
ZH: 我们买了一条透明的门帘，可以防止虫子飞进来。
EN: We bought a transparent door curtain to prevent bugs from flying in.
